room_title: Escape room "Agents of Influence" by Conundrum Escape Rooms in Durango
room_description: Agent Claussen has been working undercover to gain classified information from spy's in the four countries that are threatening the nation. Claussen, however, was compromised before he could get the information to HQ. You agents need to solve the clues he left behind in his office and send the correct kill codes to the enemies before we witness the end of the world.
